    {
        "url": "/quotes/randy_lerner_628706",
        "quote": "In U.S. sports, you tend to be pretty strictly limited by the size of your team's market. When we heard that Villa was a club here that might be available, I had a strong feeling that a team in the West Midlands could be the chance to create something very special.",
