    {
        "url": "/quotes/randy_lerner_628708",
        "quote": "While being in the right seat at the right game might create short-term reassurance, I can't get over the idea that really what people feel is that their club is being run by a group of guys who know the history, study the heritage and view Villa as a proud Victorian club in its third century.",
